posts.title: plank
posts.description:
- Always start with stretching before your workout.

- Do 1 or 2 warm-up sets before any exercise.

- Choose a weight that allows you to finish the total repetitions of each exercise.

- If you finish reps easily, increase the load a little.

- Between each repetition, take a break of about 90 seconds.
